overview.en: The decentralized image/video social platform and the digital asset TUBI designed for this purpose create a decentralized blockchain technology platform for digital video content release, sharing and transaction, enabling users to safely share images and video, sell original content and enjoy advertising revenue.
overview.zh: 去中心化的图像/视频社交平台，以及为此而设计的数字资产TUBI，打造针对数字影像内容发布、分享、交易的去中心化区块链技术平台，使用户能够安全地分享图像与视频、 出售独创的内容、享受广告收益
